h4 Key Questions
blockquote
  | Assign Key Questions to this Extraction Form in this section. A Key Question may belong to one and only one Extraction Form but an Extraction Form may have many Key Questions.
  cite Friendly Helper

= simple_form_for(efps, html: { data: { 'abide': '' } }, remote: true) do |f|
  = f.error_notification

  .form-inputs
    = f.association :key_questions_projects,
                    collection: @key_questions_projects,
                    disabled: @key_questions_projects.where.not(extraction_forms_projects_section: efps).map(&:id),
                    as: :check_boxes,
                    label: false,
                    label_method: :kq_name_and_assignment

  .form-actions
    = f.button :submit, t('save')
